      • answer

        default boolean answer(java.lang.String text,
                       boolean showAlert)
        This method is used to directly answer the CallbackQuery without having to call other methods outside this object
        Parameters:
        text - The text you would like to send in response to this CallbackQuery
        showAlert - Whether to show this as an alert or a toast. The default is a toast
        Returns:
        True if the answer was sent successfully, otherwise False
